title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Wet Ass Pocket Tee
description:
Podcasting is a team sport and the undefeated Throwing Fits squadron linking up can only mean one thing: winning. The Core 4 are in the zone and doing just that, all while debating whether golf is ass, spending too much time talking about Supreme, studying The Pimp Chronicles, salivating over Stüssy x Our Legacy’s jüicy legööchy, lampooning bozos on all sides of the “NYC is done” debate and much more for our genuinely authentic best friends behind the paywall.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
